foreignText: Ingenuas didicisse fideliter artes,   ~~Emollit mores, nec sinit esse feros.
Ut assidens implumibus pullus avis   ~~Serpentm allapsus timet,   Magis relictis; non, ut adsit, auxili   ~~Latura plus pr{ae}sentibus.
citations: Enquiry concerning Human Understanding, Sect. III.
Of scepticism with regard to the senses
